         PANDA_P         (hip yaw/roll):  kp=35  kd=5  effort=67
         KODIAK          (hip pitch/knee): kp=35 kd=7  effort=180
         KOALA_MB_ANKLE  (ankles):        kp=20  kd=3  effort=40
