  <!-- Initial-condition keyframe. qpos layout: 7 free joint (xyz + wxyz quat) + 28 joint angles.
       Joint angles in URDF/HW frame, computed from themis_rl DEFAULT_JOINT_POS via
       q_hw = sign*(q_pol - offset) per themis_rl/sim2real/joint_mapping.py. Order:
       [right_leg(6), left_leg(6), right_arm(7), left_arm(7), head(2)].
       ctrl= matches qpos joint angles so the implicit-PD actuators don't snap on activation. -->
